item.description:
SPIEGEL Interview with Singapore&rsquo;s Lee Kuan Yew&quot;It&rsquo;s Stupid to be Afraid&quot; Singapore&rsquo;s first-ever prime minister, long-time government head and current political mentor Lee Kuan Yew talks about Asia&rsquo;s rise to economic power, China&rsquo;s ambitions and the West&rsquo;s chances of staying competitive. 08.08.2005, 00.00 Uhr The elder statesman Lee: &ldquo;We run a meritocracy.&rdquo;
The elder statesman Lee: &ldquo;We run a meritocracy.&rdquo; Foto: DPA
SPIEGEL The political and economic center of gravity is moving from the West towards the East.
